WEBVTT

01:56.430 --> 01:57.840
If you don't kill it today,

01:57.840 --> 01:59.240
you will starve tonight.

02:00.640 --> 02:02.950
But I can't bring myself to do it.

02:04.280 --> 02:06.350
I can endure missing one meal.

02:06.560 --> 02:08.150
If it's not dead by tomorrow morning,

02:08.150 --> 02:09.550
you will be the one to die.

02:16.590 --> 02:18.750
See how simple it is? Take it.

02:24.630 --> 02:25.470
Kill it.

02:35.470 --> 02:38.270
Why would His Majesty
go to the General's Mansion?

02:38.470 --> 02:39.470
What do you think?

02:40.710 --> 02:44.360
I think whether His Majesty
went to the General's Mansion

02:45.240 --> 02:47.280
or to see someone else,

02:47.870 --> 02:51.000
he shouldn't have sneaked out of
the palace in the middle of the night.

02:51.000 --> 02:52.240
As a child grows up,

02:52.240 --> 02:54.750
it's inevitable for him
to have distracting thoughts.

02:54.750 --> 02:56.430
What do you plan to do, Your Highness?

02:56.430 --> 02:58.030
You can't keep a child forever
when they grow up,

02:58.030 --> 02:59.630
let alone a younger brother.

03:02.590 --> 03:05.190
What matters is not what he went to do,

03:05.870 --> 03:07.310
but rather who, with ulterior motives,

03:07.310 --> 03:08.970
guided him to do these things.

03:10.870 --> 03:12.840
Send someone to keep an eye
on the General's Mansion.

03:12.840 --> 03:14.470
I want to know everyone

03:14.680 --> 03:16.030
who comes out of there,

03:16.030 --> 03:17.750
who he meets with, and what he does,

03:17.750 --> 03:19.710
whether it's day or night.

03:19.710 --> 03:20.400
Yes.

04:12.960 --> 04:14.560
It's a token from the palace.

04:16.800 --> 04:19.160
He was the Eldest Princess's man.

04:21.160 --> 04:22.270
You shouldn't have killed him.

04:22.270 --> 04:23.390
If I hadn't killed him,

04:23.390 --> 04:25.950
should I have let him
go back and report to his master?

04:25.950 --> 04:27.160
I killed him, so what?

04:27.390 --> 04:28.590
Why so much nonsense?

04:29.270 --> 04:31.430
He followed you
from the General's Mansion to here.

04:31.430 --> 04:32.600
Now that he is dead,

04:33.190 --> 04:34.430
Liu Xie will suspect you.

04:34.430 --> 04:35.240
Fei Zheng,

04:35.560 --> 04:37.600
since when did you become so indecisive?

04:37.600 --> 04:39.630
You weren't like this before.

04:40.040 --> 04:41.600
Jinglan is not like Changmo.

04:41.600 --> 04:43.930
Killing someone won't solve the problem.

04:47.950 --> 04:49.550
When will Liu Chu come again?

04:50.070 --> 04:51.070
I will arrange it.

04:51.390 --> 04:52.650
But you must promise me

04:52.950 --> 04:54.270
not to act rashly.

04:55.000 --> 04:56.040
Are you scared?

04:56.920 --> 04:58.360
If your identity is exposed

04:58.360 --> 04:59.760
and you fail the mission,

04:59.830 --> 05:01.000
you'll be punished by the Gu poison,

05:01.000 --> 05:02.930
suffering a fate worse than death.

05:08.270 --> 05:10.470
Dispose of the body as soon as possible.

05:21.630 --> 05:22.480
Your Majesty.

05:27.270 --> 05:28.160
Your Majesty.

05:34.070 --> 05:35.800
Why don't you step down for now?

05:35.830 --> 05:36.680
Yes.

05:42.360 --> 05:44.760
Chu, what were you
thinking about just now?

05:46.870 --> 05:47.870
I...

05:49.360 --> 05:51.290
I wasn't thinking about anything.

05:52.360 --> 05:53.720
I thought you were thinking about

05:53.720 --> 05:56.050
the Princess of Changmo we met last night.

05:56.240 --> 05:57.630
How could that be?

05:58.000 --> 05:59.870
She's just a princess from Changmo.

05:59.870 --> 06:02.270
I don't even remember what she looks like.

06:04.270 --> 06:06.000
You don't remember her.

06:06.430 --> 06:08.560
I was thinking of going again tonight.

06:09.000 --> 06:09.830
Let's just drop it then.

06:09.830 --> 06:10.750
No, no.

06:13.040 --> 06:14.870
Even if we don't go see her,

06:14.870 --> 06:15.600
we...

06:15.950 --> 06:17.680
can still go drink with Xiao Chi.

06:17.680 --> 06:18.480
Right?

06:19.120 --> 06:20.430
Xiao Chi...

06:20.430 --> 06:23.030
He is getting
acupuncture treatment tonight.

06:23.190 --> 06:25.120
I'm afraid he can't drink with you.

06:25.750 --> 06:28.270
Xiao Chi's health is the top priority.

06:28.390 --> 06:30.250
Then shouldn't we go check on him?

06:32.070 --> 06:34.800
What you said makes perfect sense.

06:35.070 --> 06:36.680
Let's go then?

06:37.360 --> 06:38.159
Let's go.

06:40.950 --> 06:43.000
Where are you going, Your Majesty?

06:43.920 --> 06:44.800
Your Highness.

06:46.480 --> 06:48.159
Lord Fei and I

06:48.270 --> 06:51.040
were discussing some national affairs.

06:52.480 --> 06:55.040
I was just thinking of visiting you.

06:55.240 --> 06:57.240
That's exactly what I was thinking.

06:57.950 --> 07:00.480
I also have something to report to you.

07:03.270 --> 07:04.680
Lord Fei, it's so late.

07:05.120 --> 07:07.070
Are you planning
to stay in the palace overnight?

07:07.070 --> 07:07.870
So late?

07:10.680 --> 07:12.870
It's already... getting dark.

07:13.600 --> 07:14.680
Then I...

07:15.870 --> 07:18.070
Your Highness, Your Majesty,

07:18.240 --> 07:20.680
I shall take my leave now.

07:24.240 --> 07:26.100
Your Majesty, I'll take my leave.

07:31.720 --> 07:32.510
Sister,

07:32.870 --> 07:34.240
since you came to me so late,

07:34.240 --> 07:36.560
it must be for something very important.

07:38.560 --> 07:39.750
Nothing much.

07:40.270 --> 07:42.800
I just remembered
that the treasury ledgers

07:42.800 --> 07:44.260
haven't been shown to you.

07:44.800 --> 07:46.630
Sister, regarding the treasury,

07:46.630 --> 07:48.390
I feel most at ease leaving it to you.

07:48.390 --> 07:50.240
Besides, I know little of ledgers.

07:50.240 --> 07:51.480
Why don't you just go over them yourself?

07:51.480 --> 07:52.810
You shouldn't say that.

07:53.430 --> 07:55.070
Although we are related by blood,

07:55.070 --> 07:56.950
there is still a distinction
between ruler and subject.

07:56.950 --> 07:58.240
It is my duty.

07:58.480 --> 08:01.480
Naturally, I must report
everything to you in detail.

08:01.870 --> 08:02.750
I know.

08:02.750 --> 08:05.390
These are all the rules
left by the late Emperor.

08:05.390 --> 08:08.870
But I think our bond as siblings is deep.

08:09.070 --> 08:10.480
You are my own sister after all.

08:10.480 --> 08:12.160
Acting like this makes us distant.

08:12.160 --> 08:13.040
You should just read them yourself.

08:13.040 --> 08:13.840
Your Majesty.

08:15.040 --> 08:16.240
Do you

08:16.630 --> 08:18.490
have something else on your mind?

08:19.160 --> 08:20.480
How could I?

08:21.070 --> 08:22.360
It's so late.

08:23.240 --> 08:24.840
What else could be on my mind?

08:25.000 --> 08:27.530
If you have nothing to do,
come sit at my place.

08:28.870 --> 08:29.630
Wait.

08:34.080 --> 08:35.150
Jin Xi.

08:36.080 --> 08:37.870
We've been here for 2 hours.

08:37.960 --> 08:39.690
Who exactly are we waiting for?

08:39.750 --> 08:41.240
No, waiting for no one.

08:43.669 --> 08:47.630
Are there any changes to the plan tonight?

08:47.630 --> 08:48.550
What plan?

08:49.480 --> 08:52.030
No, nothing.

08:52.080 --> 08:53.210
Then I'm going back.

08:58.240 --> 08:59.100
Your Highness.

08:59.550 --> 09:02.150
What do you think of
that man from last night?

09:02.480 --> 09:03.360
What man?

09:03.630 --> 09:04.840
The man you said

09:04.840 --> 09:06.550
fell from the sky.

09:08.670 --> 09:10.790
I haven't seen many men in Changmo.

09:11.270 --> 09:12.840
He's different from my father.

09:12.840 --> 09:14.840
He lacks my father's martial valor.

09:15.030 --> 09:16.030
That's natural.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.960
The King of Mo is the overlord of Changmo.

09:17.960 --> 09:19.390
No man in this world

09:19.390 --> 09:20.450
can compare to him.

09:22.480 --> 09:23.440
However,

09:23.790 --> 09:25.250
he's not annoying either.

09:26.670 --> 09:27.870
Does that mean

09:28.240 --> 09:29.750
you like him a bit?

09:30.270 --> 09:31.480
How could I?

09:31.750 --> 09:32.480
Lord Fei,

09:32.480 --> 09:34.150
General Xiao, and Lieutenant Xu

09:34.150 --> 09:35.360
are not annoying either.

09:35.360 --> 09:37.160
Does that mean I like all of them?

09:40.750 --> 09:41.600
I think

09:42.030 --> 09:43.670
you quite like Lord Fei.

09:45.480 --> 09:47.840
Why do you think I like Lord Fei?

09:47.840 --> 09:49.080
I can't say for sure.

09:49.390 --> 09:52.080
It's just the way you look at him.

09:53.440 --> 09:55.840
Your Highness, I am your wedding official.

09:55.960 --> 09:56.840
Except for you,

09:56.840 --> 09:58.600
I treat everyone the same way.

09:58.870 --> 10:00.480
But I think you two...

10:00.480 --> 10:01.540
Alright, alright.

10:01.550 --> 10:03.280
Let me help you get back to rest.

10:04.630 --> 10:05.440
Okay.

10:06.030 --> 10:06.630
Let's go.

10:16.360 --> 10:18.080
What are you doing here?

10:18.240 --> 10:19.120
Waiting for you.

10:19.120 --> 10:19.980
Waiting for me?

10:20.550 --> 10:22.790
I can't find you
in the General's Mansion every day.

10:22.790 --> 10:25.250
Do you want your condition
to flare up again?

10:25.960 --> 10:26.600
I...

10:26.870 --> 10:28.200
have been busy these days.

10:28.200 --> 10:29.440
I know.

10:29.440 --> 10:29.870
Here.

10:30.030 --> 10:31.490
Take this medicine first.

10:31.630 --> 10:33.600
Take it with this.

10:36.000 --> 10:36.630
Now?

10:37.030 --> 10:37.600
Yes.

10:48.480 --> 10:49.360
This is wine?

10:49.840 --> 10:51.440
Its messenger herb is wine.

10:51.550 --> 10:52.510
Take it quickly.

11:00.960 --> 11:01.890
Come back early.

11:03.240 --> 11:04.030
Thank you.

11:16.240 --> 11:16.960
General.

11:17.150 --> 11:18.870
You checked the case files all night.

11:18.870 --> 11:20.240
Where are you going today?

11:20.240 --> 11:21.270
Just follow me.

11:21.390 --> 11:24.920
I will take you to see someone
I have respected since childhood.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.000
My Lord.

11:37.150 --> 11:38.960
You have been with me for so many years.

11:38.960 --> 11:41.360
Don't you know my rules when reading?

11:41.360 --> 11:42.080
Yes.

11:42.080 --> 11:44.630
I know you don't like to be disturbed
while reading,

11:44.630 --> 11:47.790
but there are some things
I must report to you as soon as possible.

11:47.790 --> 11:48.960
What is it?

11:48.960 --> 11:49.840
Spit it out.

11:50.120 --> 11:53.360
Xiao Chi has been checking
the Han family's case files recently.

11:53.360 --> 11:55.220
About the case files back then...

11:58.150 --> 12:01.410
This Xiao Chi is meddling in things
as soon as he comes back.

12:02.670 --> 12:04.440
Keep a close eye on him.

12:04.670 --> 12:07.440
Report to me immediately
if there is any movement.

12:07.440 --> 12:07.960
Yes.

12:12.630 --> 12:14.270
Xiao Chi.

12:26.030 --> 12:28.290
Sorry to keep you waiting, General Xiao.

12:28.480 --> 12:29.270
Lord Xue.

12:29.630 --> 12:30.440
Please sit.

12:34.200 --> 12:35.150
It's rare

12:35.150 --> 12:37.870
that you still remember
an old man like me.

12:38.030 --> 12:41.360
I've often heard of your bravery
at Tianlang Pass.

12:42.390 --> 12:43.790
I also heard a few days ago

12:44.150 --> 12:46.750
that you straightened things out
in the court.

12:46.960 --> 12:49.150
A formidable young man indeed.

12:55.390 --> 12:57.870
How is your health recently, Lord Xue?

12:58.240 --> 12:59.550
I'm an old man now,

12:59.840 --> 13:02.550
so my health is definitely
not what it used to be.

13:02.840 --> 13:04.600
I know a physician

13:04.790 --> 13:06.120
with excellent medical skills.

13:06.120 --> 13:07.630
She can take a look at you.

13:08.150 --> 13:09.150
A physician?

13:09.840 --> 13:11.150
Coincidentally,

13:11.550 --> 13:12.960
this physician's

13:13.550 --> 13:14.910
surname is Han.

13:17.390 --> 13:20.080
Just speak your mind, General Xiao.

13:20.910 --> 13:21.960
I wonder if you

13:21.960 --> 13:24.320
still remember the Han family case?

13:26.030 --> 13:27.630
The Han family?

13:28.600 --> 13:30.790
That is an old case from years ago.

13:31.080 --> 13:33.080
Why bring it up suddenly?

13:33.080 --> 13:35.150
I've been investigating this case recently

13:35.150 --> 13:37.480
and found many suspicious points.

13:37.480 --> 13:40.000
So I came to consult you.

13:40.960 --> 13:42.080
I see.

13:43.270 --> 13:45.870
However, since it is an old case,

13:46.390 --> 13:49.200
I don't remember it very clearly.

13:57.030 --> 13:58.030
Physician Han,

13:58.790 --> 14:01.120
I am here to get medicine
for Her Highness.

14:09.550 --> 14:10.550
Three times a day.

14:10.630 --> 14:12.430
Serve it to Her Highness on time.

14:14.480 --> 14:15.840
Thank you, Physician Han.

14:15.840 --> 14:16.790
Later,

14:16.790 --> 14:19.450
I will go and check on
Her Highness's condition.

14:23.240 --> 14:23.960
Thank you,

14:24.480 --> 14:25.630
Physician Han.

14:26.200 --> 14:26.790
Jin Xi!

14:34.030 --> 14:35.390
Such an erratic pulse.

14:37.870 --> 14:38.720
Lord Xue,

14:39.080 --> 14:40.440
could the Han family's case

14:40.440 --> 14:42.300
have been a wrongful conviction?

14:45.030 --> 14:46.480
The case was closed.

14:46.670 --> 14:49.480
Whether it was unjust or not,
it's all in the past.

14:50.390 --> 14:51.480
General Xiao,

14:51.480 --> 14:53.080
let me offer you some advice.

14:53.440 --> 14:55.080
Don't ask what you shouldn't ask,

14:55.080 --> 14:56.750
and don't meddle in what you shouldn't.

14:56.750 --> 14:58.840
That is the way to be a good official.

15:01.670 --> 15:03.070
I appreciate the advice.

15:05.240 --> 15:07.080
Since you can't remember,

15:08.000 --> 15:09.960
pardon my intrusion today.

15:10.550 --> 15:11.950
Take care, General Xiao.

15:12.270 --> 15:12.960
Farewell.

15:33.360 --> 15:33.890
General,

15:34.270 --> 15:35.750
is this the person you mentioned

15:35.750 --> 15:37.610
you respected in your childhood?

15:38.360 --> 15:39.790
I haven't seen him for many years.

15:39.790 --> 15:41.320
He has indeed changed a lot.

15:41.750 --> 15:42.790
Let's go back first

15:42.790 --> 15:43.650
and make plans.

15:43.670 --> 15:44.030
Okay.

16:02.480 --> 16:03.440
You're awake.

16:05.870 --> 16:07.510
Here, drink the medicine.

16:09.240 --> 16:10.630
What's wrong with me?

16:10.870 --> 16:12.080
You are poisoned.

16:13.150 --> 16:14.200
Poisoned?

16:18.750 --> 16:19.550
Jin Xi,

16:20.200 --> 16:21.510
I know who you are.

16:21.870 --> 16:23.150
You know who I am too.

16:24.200 --> 16:25.630
Since you don't want to acknowledge me,

16:25.630 --> 16:26.750
I won't force you.

16:27.360 --> 16:29.420
You must have your own difficulties.

16:34.670 --> 16:39.670
Can you counteract this poison?

16:39.670 --> 16:40.670
I'm not sure.

16:41.870 --> 16:43.960
If you want to completely
counteract this poison,

16:43.960 --> 16:46.670
you must tell me everything
about how you were poisoned

16:46.670 --> 16:48.600
and how it flared up in detail.

16:48.840 --> 16:50.900
Otherwise, there's nothing I can do.

16:56.600 --> 16:57.510
Physician Han,

16:57.510 --> 16:59.670
don't waste any more time on me.

16:59.750 --> 17:00.600
My poison

17:01.360 --> 17:02.510
has nothing

17:03.320 --> 17:04.829
to do with you.

17:04.829 --> 17:05.310
You...

17:10.440 --> 17:12.369
Better to live badly than die well.

17:12.400 --> 17:13.680
Only by staying alive

17:14.000 --> 17:15.480
can you do more things.

17:22.589 --> 17:24.319
I don't really want to cure you.

17:24.680 --> 17:25.829
I just enjoy

17:26.400 --> 17:27.680
unraveling symptoms.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.830
I have nothing to do these days anyway.

17:29.830 --> 17:32.630
If I get an idea,
I'll prescribe you some medicine.

17:35.350 --> 17:37.680
Then thank you in advance, Physician Han.

17:50.550 --> 17:51.400
Young Master Wang,

17:51.400 --> 17:52.830
see which one you like

17:52.830 --> 17:54.360
and take whatever you want.

17:56.750 --> 17:58.030
This stuff tastes awful.

17:58.030 --> 17:59.590
How dare you sell it?

17:59.750 --> 18:00.880
Don't! Don't!

18:01.200 --> 18:02.030
Young Master Wang,

18:02.030 --> 18:04.000
I don't know which one tastes good

18:04.000 --> 18:05.350
or bad either.

18:05.480 --> 18:07.340
If you don't think it tastes good,

18:07.590 --> 18:09.200
how about I compensate you?

18:09.680 --> 18:10.750
You piece of trash.

18:11.030 --> 18:14.510
I am the only son
of Wang Ruhai, the Chief Minister.

18:14.830 --> 18:16.350
Do I care about your petty cash?

18:16.350 --> 18:17.880
What do you want me to do?

18:18.000 --> 18:19.440
Eat all of these,

18:19.830 --> 18:20.750
and we'll call it even.

18:20.750 --> 18:21.270
Ah?

18:22.350 --> 18:23.070
No, no!

18:23.070 --> 18:23.880
Feed him.

18:24.030 --> 18:24.790
Alright.

18:26.960 --> 18:28.590
Young Master Wang, please don't!

18:28.590 --> 18:29.650
Young Master Wang!

18:29.960 --> 18:30.880
What are you looking at?

18:30.880 --> 18:32.210
Never seen this before?

18:35.030 --> 18:37.480
Hurry and eat!

18:37.480 --> 18:38.350
I'll come back for it later.

18:38.350 --> 18:40.150
I heard a new restaurant opened.

18:40.200 --> 18:41.440
-Let's go.
-Let's go try it.

18:41.440 --> 18:42.480
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

18:42.480 --> 18:43.480
Enjoy your meal.

18:43.550 --> 18:44.830
Madam, bring me a pot of wine.

18:44.830 --> 18:45.760
Coming right up.

18:50.750 --> 18:51.200
Here.

18:51.830 --> 18:52.750
Here's the wine.

18:52.750 --> 18:54.550
Young Master Wang is here to have a drink.

18:54.550 --> 18:55.880
-Get out!
-Get lost!

18:57.480 --> 18:58.750
Don't leave!

18:59.160 --> 19:00.270
Please don't leave!

19:00.270 --> 19:01.070
You haven't paid yet!

19:01.070 --> 19:02.160
What money?

19:02.640 --> 19:04.680
He is the son of Lord Wang,
the Chief Minister.

19:04.680 --> 19:06.280
You'd better serve him well.

19:09.680 --> 19:11.550
So it is you, Young Master Wang.

19:11.680 --> 19:14.270
Please, have a seat. Please.

19:17.590 --> 19:19.790
What would you like to drink,
Young Master Wang?

19:19.790 --> 19:22.400
The best wine you have here, of course.

19:22.440 --> 19:24.270
Okay, I'll bring it right away.

19:30.110 --> 19:31.000
Who goes there?

19:31.350 --> 19:32.640
Young Master Wang
has booked the whole place.

19:32.640 --> 19:33.880
No admittance.

19:34.270 --> 19:35.670
Which Young Master Wang?

19:35.880 --> 19:39.030
The son of Lord Wang Ruhai,
the current Chief Minister.

19:41.830 --> 19:42.510
So what?

19:43.880 --> 19:46.270
It's a misunderstanding.

19:46.400 --> 19:48.680
This is my good friend.

19:48.750 --> 19:50.550
She came specifically to see me.

19:51.270 --> 19:52.070
Come here.

19:55.640 --> 19:57.550
Oh, Young Master Wang,

19:57.550 --> 19:59.790
this is the best wine in our restaurant.

19:59.960 --> 20:01.680
Let me pour you a cup.

20:03.640 --> 20:04.680
Let me toast you

20:04.680 --> 20:05.680
to apologize.

20:06.640 --> 20:08.110
Who do you think you are?

20:08.110 --> 20:09.710
How dare you offer me a toast?

20:12.830 --> 20:13.890
Young Master Wang!

20:14.240 --> 20:15.270
Who are you

20:15.350 --> 20:16.510
to dare mess with me?

20:16.790 --> 20:18.520
I am General Xiao's physician.

20:19.750 --> 20:21.880
General, what are you thinking about?

20:21.880 --> 20:22.960
I was just thinking,

20:22.960 --> 20:24.550
if Wang Ruhai's son

20:24.550 --> 20:26.480
is this arrogant and overbearing,

20:26.830 --> 20:28.070
his father

20:28.880 --> 20:30.680
is surely no better at court.

20:31.640 --> 20:33.270
What do you mean?

20:34.640 --> 20:35.480
Lord Xue

20:35.750 --> 20:37.240
might have been coerced.

20:37.270 --> 20:38.270
Coerced?

20:39.750 --> 20:40.920
He must know the inside story.

20:40.920 --> 20:41.350
Go.

20:47.000 --> 20:47.830
Lord Xue.

20:51.750 --> 20:52.550
Lord Xue.

20:58.110 --> 20:59.640
We are still a step too late.

20:59.750 --> 21:01.030
In broad daylight,

21:01.030 --> 21:02.490
they dared to silence him.

21:03.070 --> 21:03.880
General,

21:04.350 --> 21:07.030
it seems the Han family's case
is not simple.

21:09.720 --> 21:11.200
If you let him escape,

21:11.400 --> 21:13.000
Lord Zhang will definitely
kill your whole family.

21:13.000 --> 21:13.790
Yes.

21:14.240 --> 21:15.350
Lord Zhang.

21:16.200 --> 21:17.270
Zhang Ruizhong.

21:20.240 --> 21:21.880
It hurts! It hurts!

21:24.000 --> 21:25.350
You useless thing,

21:25.350 --> 21:26.680
you only bring me shame.

21:34.070 --> 21:35.000
My Lord,

21:35.000 --> 21:37.480
the young master's hand wound
must stay dry.

21:37.480 --> 21:40.030
He should refrain from
washing his hands for the next few days.

21:40.030 --> 21:41.640
Thank you for your hard work.

21:41.680 --> 21:43.210
You are too polite, My Lord.

21:43.480 --> 21:44.270
I will take my leave.

21:44.270 --> 21:45.070
Hmm.

21:46.030 --> 21:46.510
Please.

21:46.510 --> 21:47.110
Thank you.

21:52.640 --> 21:54.480
What a disgrace.

21:54.830 --> 21:56.070
Next time you cause trouble,

21:56.070 --> 21:57.640
I'll send you to the estate!

22:01.830 --> 22:02.920
Father.

22:03.270 --> 22:04.830
I know I was wrong.

22:05.270 --> 22:06.750
But you can't stand by

22:06.750 --> 22:08.410
and watch your son be bullied.

22:08.590 --> 22:09.590
Advisor.

22:09.590 --> 22:12.000
Find someone to shut down
that restaurant tomorrow.

22:12.000 --> 22:12.730
Restaurant?

22:12.880 --> 22:14.880
It's the newly popular restaurant.

22:15.240 --> 22:16.840
The owner's surname is Tang.

22:16.880 --> 22:17.880
She is a woman.

22:18.830 --> 22:19.640
A woman?

22:19.750 --> 22:20.440
My Lord.

22:20.640 --> 22:21.830
If you ask me,

22:21.880 --> 22:23.880
this matter is probably not simple.

22:23.880 --> 22:25.210
Think about it, My Lord.

22:25.480 --> 22:26.440
She is just a woman.

22:26.440 --> 22:28.030
How much trouble can she cause?

22:28.030 --> 22:31.160
Ultimately, it's her backer
who is powerful.

22:31.160 --> 22:31.920
Exactly.

22:32.310 --> 22:34.830
That little wench dared to bully me.

22:35.070 --> 22:35.750
I heard

22:35.880 --> 22:37.640
She is Xiao Chi's physician.

22:38.400 --> 22:39.030
Huh?

22:41.960 --> 22:42.960
Xiao Chi?

22:46.680 --> 22:48.880
He just never stops.

23:09.030 --> 23:09.830
My Lord.

23:10.350 --> 23:11.790
The matter is settled.

23:13.350 --> 23:15.270
Xue...

23:15.880 --> 23:18.030
to make you shut up forever,

23:19.550 --> 23:21.550
I had to do this to you.

23:22.480 --> 23:24.310
I have sent Judge Xue's family

23:24.310 --> 23:25.270
out of the city overnight.

23:25.270 --> 23:27.640
Not even the gods can find them.

23:29.270 --> 23:31.680
Did you give them
enough compensation money?

23:31.680 --> 23:33.480
Yes, a lot.

23:36.640 --> 23:39.240
Xue shouldn't have died.

23:39.880 --> 23:41.160
But it just so happens

23:41.510 --> 23:43.160
that Xiao Chi found him.

23:43.680 --> 23:45.480
So he had no one else to blame.

23:46.590 --> 23:49.030
My Lord, you are merciful.

23:49.030 --> 23:50.830
Lord Xue's spirit in heaven

23:50.830 --> 23:53.160
will also appreciate your kindness.

23:55.270 --> 23:56.590
However,

23:56.830 --> 23:58.480
that kid Xiao Chi

23:59.160 --> 24:01.640
will probably keep investigating.

24:02.160 --> 24:03.000
Yeah, My Lord,

24:03.000 --> 24:04.790
if he doesn't give up easily,

24:04.790 --> 24:07.190
it really will be a bit difficult
to handle.

24:08.680 --> 24:12.640
You should know
how to handle this kind of thing.

24:13.720 --> 24:15.030
Just leave it to me.

24:15.680 --> 24:16.940
Rest assured, My Lord.

24:17.790 --> 24:18.680
Very good.

24:19.000 --> 24:20.880
Go and get your reward.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.440
Thank you, My Lord.

24:52.640 --> 24:53.900
Why did you come alone?

24:54.880 --> 24:55.810
Where is Liu Chu?

24:56.880 --> 24:59.030
Recently, the Eldest Princess

24:59.030 --> 25:01.070
has been keeping
His Majesty up all night talking.

25:01.070 --> 25:03.480
He hasn't had any chance
to leave the palace at all.

25:03.480 --> 25:04.550
Useless.

25:05.640 --> 25:08.100
We need patience
to achieve our great cause.

25:09.400 --> 25:11.270
Don't worry. If there's a chance,

25:11.270 --> 25:12.590
I'll bring him over right away.

25:12.590 --> 25:14.200
I don't have much time left.

25:16.550 --> 25:17.480
What do you mean?

25:19.400 --> 25:20.480
After you left,

25:20.790 --> 25:22.920
the Hall Master developed a Gu poison.

25:22.960 --> 25:25.750
I must complete the mission
to get the antidote.

25:26.030 --> 25:28.290
Otherwise, it's a fate worse than death.

25:28.960 --> 25:30.290
In the King of Mo's eyes,

25:30.960 --> 25:33.420
we are nothing but tools
for his great cause.

25:34.550 --> 25:35.350
Recently,

25:36.200 --> 25:38.930
I've been showing signs
of the poison flaring up.

25:39.880 --> 25:41.240
What about Physician Han?

25:41.240 --> 25:42.900
Why don't you ask her for help?

25:44.680 --> 25:46.720
I can't tell her the truth.

25:47.000 --> 25:47.790
Besides,

25:48.440 --> 25:50.040
the antidote to the Gu poison

25:50.750 --> 25:52.810
is only possessed by the Hall Master.

25:52.880 --> 25:53.750
I understand.

25:54.590 --> 25:57.960
I'll hasten Liu Chu's marriage
with the Princess.

25:58.350 --> 25:59.350
Once the mission is completed

25:59.350 --> 26:00.750
and you get the antidote,

26:02.640 --> 26:04.590
just return to Changmo.

26:15.880 --> 26:17.550
I noticed you were coughing today,

26:17.550 --> 26:20.010
so I changed an ingredient
in your medicine.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.200
Well...

27:02.070 --> 27:05.880
I did something very impulsive today.

27:07.270 --> 27:08.030
I know.

27:10.720 --> 27:11.310
You know?

27:12.030 --> 27:13.400
I was there today.

27:13.680 --> 27:15.940
You intimidated all of them by yourself,

27:16.070 --> 27:17.680
so I didn't step in.

27:18.590 --> 27:20.790
Will I cause trouble for Ms. Tang?

27:21.880 --> 27:23.270
Isn't it a bit too late

27:23.270 --> 27:24.640
to say this now?

27:28.830 --> 27:29.560
Don't worry.

27:29.750 --> 27:32.680
If she finds it troublesome,
she'll leave on her own.

27:32.790 --> 27:34.550
You are too heartless.

27:35.240 --> 27:36.270
Me, heartless?

27:36.550 --> 27:38.960
After all, Ms. Tang followed us
all the way from Tianlang Pass

27:38.960 --> 27:40.110
to the capital.

27:40.270 --> 27:41.880
She arranged food and lodging
along the way.

27:41.880 --> 27:43.000
Just for this,

27:43.880 --> 27:45.740
you should show her some concern.

27:49.200 --> 27:51.960
I already had Chengfeng
give her the money.

27:52.070 --> 27:54.470
I don't want to have anything
to do with her.

27:54.920 --> 27:55.720
As for you,

27:56.790 --> 27:57.790
stop showing off.

27:58.480 --> 27:59.640
If something like this happens,

27:59.640 --> 28:00.510
who else will take care of it if not me?

28:00.510 --> 28:01.270
Me.

28:04.030 --> 28:06.480
I mean, I'm here in the capital.

28:06.680 --> 28:09.160
If you need anything, you can come to me.

28:23.830 --> 28:24.590
Your Highness.

28:24.590 --> 28:25.270
Jin Xi.

28:27.030 --> 28:28.350
You don't look well.

28:28.350 --> 28:29.550
Are you feeling sick?

28:30.000 --> 28:30.550
No,

28:30.830 --> 28:31.630
it's nothing.

28:31.830 --> 28:32.350
Oh.

28:32.640 --> 28:33.590
That's good.

28:38.640 --> 28:40.240
What are you thinking about?

28:41.830 --> 28:42.790
Nothing.

28:45.550 --> 28:46.270
Are you

28:46.510 --> 28:47.640
homesick?

28:48.110 --> 28:48.640
Yes.

28:49.240 --> 28:50.440
I miss my father.

28:50.960 --> 28:53.350
I've never been away from him for so long.

28:55.270 --> 28:58.270
Besides the King of Mo,
is there no one else you miss?

28:59.200 --> 29:01.640
Who else would I miss besides my father?

29:02.440 --> 29:03.590
I can tell you're tired.

29:03.590 --> 29:04.720
You should go to sleep.

29:04.720 --> 29:06.480
I'll rest in a bit too.
